{"tid":278680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港排第六】日本人票選外國美食十強　雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻榜上無名","createTime":"2017-06-10T15:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T11:54:51.000Z","uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f90f984378529f8d717c7674f08d0683319728d6","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"【香港排第六】日本人票選外國美食十強　雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻榜上無名<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20170610/20050931?_ga=2.163261439.2125625850.1497106330-915121093.1482931786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ffood%2Fart%2F20170610%2F20050931%3F_ga%3D2.163261439.2125625850.1497106330-915121093.1482931786&d=wBcafSBMJWD7cDcEYs37INtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=55f17261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ffood%2Fart%2F20170610%2F20050931%3F_ga%3D2.163261439.2125625850.1497106330-915121093.1482931786&h=e4a76da5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20170610/20050931?_ga=2.163261439.2125625850.1497106330-915121093.1482931786</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次日本樂天旅遊網票選外國美食十強，香港地道小食如雞蛋仔、缽仔糕和蛋撻都榜上無名。<br />\n<br />\n香港人經常到日本尋美食，但究竟在日本人眼中甚麼才是美食呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">最近日本樂天旅遊網請當地人用自己神聖一票，票選外國美食十強，調查在4月5日至13日期間進行，訪問了1,155人</span>，在芸芸國家中，法國、夏威夷、越南及新加坡都入圍十強，但三甲不入。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣以166票獲票選第一位，結果不太意外，其實日本人與香港人一樣，都喜歡皮薄餡靚又多汁的小籠包、街頭巷尾都有的滷肉飯、入味的紅燒牛肉麵、蚵仔煎和臭豆腐。</span>意大利就以約50票之差，以119票屈居第二，這比較出人意表，可能香港人較熟悉的意大利菜就只有薄餅和意粉，但日本人就覺得卡邦尼意粉很有質感，也喜歡Tiramisu。韓風亦吹到日本，第三名是韓國，不過日本人喜歡的韓食與香港人不同，燒肉沒份兒，日本人反而比較喜歡健康的人參雞湯，而正所謂臭味相投，同樣喜歡生吃的日本人，亦有選醬油蟹。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港似乎被冠上「惡魔之名」了，皆因香港在66票之下排第六，名副其實的「666」</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">以為日本人一定力推香港小食？大錯特錯了，原來日本人比較喜歡香港的魚翅和鮑魚粥，並將它們放在首選；反而最地道的小食如雞蛋仔、缽仔糕、蛋撻等就隻字不提，</span>所以下次如果有日本朋友到港，真的要帶他們好好試試香港小食。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰盧逸文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a236d92023c2c4ea107320bd16c3d2ba75512356","tid":278680,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"666<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c1b7d3c801f9c69d3e6c618bdda3627a385f02","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"cc 台 :「依 1155 日本人,  肯定無係被人收買架啦」  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美食天堂 都被評第 6 咋 ? 唔撚係呀 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3a19d3426ad37f50a2f6ddc99d1d7ff685f7f7","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"仆街日本仔食過 香港啲龍津既<del>垃圾</del>魚蛋 燒賣未呀 ? <br />\n<br />\n辣殺日本仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64719473cfd4fff80f88c2adb1904539f47cd27b","tid":278680,"uid":54183,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddd4356002fdf4b01bea02a9e0dc2e97d031b27c","tid":278680,"uid":75452,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻 <br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野不嬲都係垃圾劣食<br />\n真係得港豬先會中意</blockquote><br />\n食既係細個既童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc34e8111cefade801f6dfbadeccb1750ac4c9f","tid":278680,"uid":54183,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ad0c21ae231ba9160967da8d44fef8a2f248994","tid":278680,"uid":34899,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"日狗鐘意黎香港食咩 wfc"},{"pid":"b7d3cc4cddd5df84303de0dece4345329eed4cd1","tid":278680,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"雞蛋仔垃圾 無技巧可言"},{"pid":"e636aee176831a2409a6cb0259dd421635a662a2","tid":278680,"uid":79410,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻 <br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野不嬲都係垃圾劣食<br />\n真係得港豬先會中意</blockquote><br />\n食既係細個既童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都ON99，食回憶食童年，食壯年唔撚得？<br />\n<br />\n過左童年就無左果種味道就唔係美食啦<br />\n呢種叫劣食</blockquote><br />\n雞蛋仔砵仔糕都係一堆粉漿開出黎。真係唔知做乜做左小食代表。<br />\n蛋撻又唔夠葡撻好食。<br />\n食魚蛋燒賣牛雜好過。"},{"pid":"cf179ccdd8a884b2f35ab8d8440efc4f6fcc12e2","tid":278680,"uid":54183,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0c22c67bdb1f232f092ab9679233a5a76dd0866","tid":278680,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"魚翅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3942f1c66add76cd4e16881729170928ebf5f8","tid":278680,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"港畜玻璃心 碎滿地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d285d17cff139c7c5680de972392a0ecf0d296","tid":278680,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"唔岩日本仔口味 問鬼佬可能就中意"},{"pid":"b286ad3362d86c42906b579957587e0f798f8a3c","tid":278680,"uid":6435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedB