oji\" /> 有冇連登仔想搞街頭外國遊客訪問 問下身處香港既遊客有咩見解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4767db5fef466e96d3301ca2d59a5f87f74ff550","tid":278680,"uid":92656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cc 台 :「依 1155 日本人,  肯定無係被人收買架啦」  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美食天堂 都被評第 6 咋 ? 唔撚係呀 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美食天堂個朵關香港本土小食撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90163d9397d2bd11ea298c1e4249c275a22e42f","tid":278680,"uid":32707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:07:15.000Z","msg":"香港邊有野好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb0e264528c3b0888621ea799f5e33d0ab793c7","tid":278680,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得台灣食乜嘢都好油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cc8de934bc3b501612582df315df09caf4ee97","tid":278680,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻 <br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野不嬲都係垃圾劣食<br />\n真係得港豬先會中意</blockquote><br />\n食既係細個既童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都ON99，食回憶食童年，食壯年唔撚得？<br />\n<br />\n過左童年就無左果種味道就唔係美食啦<br />\n呢種叫劣食</blockquote><br />\n雞蛋仔砵仔糕都係一堆粉漿開出黎。真係唔知做乜做左小食代表。<br />\n蛋撻又唔夠葡撻好食。<br />\n食魚蛋燒賣牛雜好過。</blockquote><br />\n好食粉漿貨日本大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n葡撻&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;蛋撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e8702923f383876ab32b0df0c0206f4950f037","tid":278680,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗撻<br />\n另外兩樣野都唔特別鐘意食<br />\n但點解冇提全世界人都指定食既點心？</blockquote><br />\n蝦餃燒買有阿摩尼亞味 水晶蝦 冇味 一係就強國點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf77e9406c9017e70aaf3aa6b4dfbad6fb3870dc","tid":278680,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"一千個人代表所有日本人對全世界小食的喜好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁選舉委員會都可以代表全香港人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3acd669effbdc5b9a3c46e720da680f945135df","tid":278680,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻 <br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野不嬲都係垃圾劣食<br />\n真係得港豬先會中意</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真 仲要咁多年都無乜變化 反觀架仔d拉麵愈做愈出色 湯底間間唔同各有特色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5595de0a351e4c880fb228fe7e50fe20eb2abe72","tid":278680,"uid":2867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港豬依家折墮到要用街邊最市井，最cheap既劣食（即係平時只有窮撚／街童食開果D街頭走鬼檔劣食）<br />\n黎代表香港美食，陰鳩功<br />\n<br />\n正正經經係一般酒樓／餐廳係叫唔到呢D劣食<br />\n因為真係上唔到大枱<br />\n<br />\n唔提意大利，近近地，唔該港唔望下台灣先<br />\n小籠包，滷肉飯，牛肉麵　　　<br />\n<br />\n全部都唔係豪華野，甚至可以話係cheap野<br />\n但起碼正經過港豬果D劣食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真 唔係香港人咪撚出聲啦 <br />\n一早認得你個名架啦"},{"pid":"fe143869d638323b9453baad62ce5cbfd35b4f1d","tid":278680,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一千個人代表所有日本人對全世界小食的喜好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁選舉委員會都可以代表全香港人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n得個千幾中意台灣咋<br />\n淨返個幾億人一定最愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffb35292b05862d2c898b96f5da9d939d0ebca2","tid":278680,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"雞蛋仔蛋撻係劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3616ab5a886d18052a167ef19dd9fdf5cbe0259b","tid":278680,"uid":12911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"理撚得你 雞蛋仔格仔餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8f71c27ce4f6f2b84316bc2d254a431e91effe","tid":278680,"uid":148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"家陣缽仔糕、白糖糕呢啲想搵嚟食都難<br />\n以前細細個街邊總有一間賣呢啲,而家一街金舖藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4d6789df869d5001bc8228479b9f4a7a4569b2","tid":278680,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:41:12.000Z","msg":"而家d雞蛋仔變左粗製濫造,又搞咩唔同味既都多撚餘<br />\n<br />\n想搵間好食既都唔知係邊搵<br />\n<br />\n但格仔餅去低調高手買真係好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你既然推得台灣牛肉麵,港式車仔麵有唔少都屌打佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0335d8b7521521da9ca278e8c1886ce0e319bd44","tid":278680,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:43:09.000Z","msg":"香港小食真係又垃圾又貴<br />\n我自己1年都唔會食一次"},{"pid":"1b90d6c0aa93b4ff2ed1ae067cd333394d08c7ce","tid":278680,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一千個人代表所有日本人對全世界小食的喜好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁選舉委員會都可以代表全香港人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得讀好啲書入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6555af9c3a856eccd0db6f2d07fefa990174d3c8","tid":278680,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c0ed260fafff29920170528bfc688bf788debe1","tid":278680,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:03:42.000Z","msg":"夏威夷有乜食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7b2e4e7c89b400db9de5698e5d0a207e1d225c","tid":278680,"uid":36510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:04:40.000Z","msg":"小籠包係台灣菜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣野普遍都太油,<br />\n滷肉飯d肉肥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺台北我覺得好食嘅餐廳全部唔係台菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7b64acfffdb8545bf153b98e3d505a2158c833","tid":278680,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻 <br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野不嬲都係垃圾劣食<br />\n真係得港豬先會中意</blockquote><br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002602421e2634c08c33489978278bae8ab71f4f","tid":278680,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:06:00.000Z","msg":"同類日本鯛魚燒秒撚左雞蛋仔啦"},{"pid":"11a391fe1cca50a59f4ad2dd9c1827f66d0eb757","tid":278680,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同類日本鯛魚燒秒撚左雞蛋仔啦</blockquote><br />\n中肯<br />\n人地日本連便利店d野食都好食過唔知香港幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91162e6396a37c695f53024449a823e704640ec0","tid":278680,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f0099e2eebcbecbb141ea43a8e8de222bc59ebc","tid":278680,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:57:36.000Z","msg":"香港人都搵唔到好食既燒賣魚蛋<br />\n點推介比人👁👁"},{"pid":"3d80d8cc63768af12e3cdd19035f4fb3f7c09e2d","tid":278680,"uid":84263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:01:02.000Z","msg":"踩港撚全面進場！"},{"pid":"473797948fa55999ba36e0a3c5756a3d0486e71e","tid":278680,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:02:25.000Z","msg":"牛雜屌打全部啦<br />\n喂 咩雞蛋仔砵仔糕企開啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a1d3fa18f63faae6d4dc5a14c6645739daaf90a","tid":278680,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:21:13.000Z","msg":"台灣蚵仔煎,識嘅所有人去台灣食過,冇一個人係話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7e7ed53729bfebf0ce4ff5b8267e6b986fe9ff","tid":278680,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T20:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人都搵唔到好食既燒賣魚蛋<br />\n點推介比人👁👁</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bef0cb2aa4a736e3ae2655866f4d2dffbf9ce9","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理撚得你 雞蛋仔格仔餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加埋砵仔糕+碗仔翅+魚肉菜 我超中意食 但好食唔係度度有"},{"pid":"ffc88d84c355fcba7358e4f0b59d3f24e75bbdef","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同類日本鯛魚燒秒撚左雞蛋仔啦</blockquote><br />\n中肯<br />\n人地日本連便利店d野食都好食過唔知香港幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺 個皮通常冇味 食入面涵<br />\n但雞蛋仔蛋香 格仔餅蛋香+漿 好鬼正<br />\n煮法又可以唔同 有機整 有炭燒<br />\n不過要指定舖頭先係人間美食 仲要趁熱食"},{"pid":"9514a48c3d2bf482e6497524c7085b545a04f4a4","tid":278680,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:38:46.000Z","msg":"點解tw 用小龍包牛肉面<br />\nhk 唔用點心同牛腩面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3a5124b3c1967611ed80025bbef0cdd9430f4d","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣蚵仔煎,識嘅所有人去台灣食過,冇一個人係話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得好難食<br />\n台灣臭豆腐好食過香港既 我受唔到香港落啲漿<br />\n同埋香香雞好鬼正"},{"pid":"e5a127766769193354c5d600c88f841af11b3de8","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人都搵唔到好食既燒賣魚蛋<br />\n點推介比人👁👁</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好食魚蛋燒賣做唔住 成本貴"},{"pid":"1d521a6314104292a0d5fd02a7967f7fa1ba469c","tid":278680,"uid":50186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:48:09.000Z","msg":"價錢平就係劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf605327ae065ea59969245ba6ae798278045fe","tid":278680,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:54:43.000Z","msg":"港畜不嬲食開屎<br />\n咁都入到頭十<br />\n日本人好畀面了"},{"pid":"5fe5917367233c3be5c307ffe51944384ea30e09","tid":278680,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:07:06.000Z","msg":"宜家香港有本土特色既野食好多都搞到不倫不類<br />\n咩綠茶燕窩蛋撻 幾十款味既雞蛋仔 芝士拉絲煲仔飯 空氣麵包 酒樓點心愈黎愈難食<br />\n都無邊間真係專注做好果樣野食既味道<br />\n做起左果d茶餐廳又愈黎愈難食<br />\n好多食完都唔想再食第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85c0cc9b88a4193e994dffe2687b52d819a74ec","tid":278680,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"洗咩咁在意日本仔鐘唔鐘意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又唔係為左佢而生存"},{"pid":"e8e3dd8dbe48339351d6912c48206a63e16aa079","tid":278680,"uid":3581,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:02:56.000Z","msg":"香港有咩好食, 諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n劣食就推介到"},{"pid":"c0f8c76105180344d2d965c2ac003e82cfb17c02","tid":278680,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港人都搵唔到好食既燒賣魚蛋<br />\n點推介比人👁👁</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好食魚蛋燒賣做唔住 成本貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食過日本d燒賣, 雖然有少少唔同<br />\n<br />\n但係都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6064a3fdab078be6d3f6329f96d1f291f89eba52","tid":278680,"uid":73849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞蛋仔缽仔糕蛋撻 <br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野不嬲都係垃圾劣食<br />\n真係得港豬先會中意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋仔比起後兩者相對簡單，但係整得有心機都可以好大分別，例如慳唔慳個漿、係咪整得外面嗰浸得個硬字，<br />\n蛋撻同砵仔糕都係手工嘢，當然有好多係求其整，但識揀舖頭買都好明顯食得出有分別，<br />\n唔知你係不嬲睇唔起，定不嬲食開啲唔好食嘅，先有不嬲都係垃圾劣食呢個睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最唔明點解鍾意食就係港豬"},{"pid":"ae54db131a569c5e9c0fe0b784ef2a13ae5c2a20","tid":278680,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"個記者一定係食屎大<br />\n咩叫沒有份兒<br />\n無份咪無份<br />\n咩叫份兒？<br />\n腦裝屎"},{"pid":"fb8911030778f6ea8db96557ed81137beab62ef5","tid":278680,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:47:17.000Z","msg":"現在又流行整埋啲咩抹茶雪糕雞蛋仔<br />\n但又學唔到日本嗰種懂得融合嘅水平同精神<br />\n啲雪糕都係普通到唔普通嘅質素<br />\n再求其加上件雞蛋仔就算<br />\n完全冇獨家技巧<br />\n搞到不倫不類，雪糕同個雞蛋仔係完全唔夾<br />\n搞到值得推介嘅傳統hardcore雞蛋仔愈嚟愈少<br />\n扮上菜嘅雞蛋仔又完全唔掂"},{"pid":"6583db4b76a96b3d3823c8e9adc7ed99d4b8bd6d","tid":278680,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"見到謝霆鋒個雞蛋仔都知咩事啦"},{"pid":"069c57d770211e46a98f205e152ea8c78fd94f14","tid":278680,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:53:33.000Z","msg":"得罪講句喇<br />\n香港已經玩完<br />\n唔關政治事或者住屋問題<br />\n係成個文化層出晒事<br />\n而係香港啲人學埋晒其他地方唔好嘅嘢<br />\n介紹吃喝玩樂嘅傳媒就學咗台灣嘩眾取寵<br />\n料理就學韓國嘅快速同無厘頭嘅cross over扮上菜嘅文化<br />\n又學晒日本嘅援交同PTGF"},{"pid":"3d01cfb5362fe0b6dce979f0133b2671c2a12500","tid":278680,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句喇<br />\n香港已經玩完<br />\n唔關政治事或者住屋問題<br />\n而係成個文化層出晒事<br />\n現在香港啲人學埋晒其他地方唔好嘅嘢<br />\n介紹吃喝玩樂嘅傳媒就學咗台灣嘩眾取寵<br />\n料理就學韓國嘅快速同無厘頭嘅cross over扮上菜嘅文化<br />\n又學晒日本嘅援交同PTGF</blockquote>"},{"pid":"29699270f856a27362054b35db2470a7fb6ed642","tid":278680,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:55:51.000Z","msg":"平心而論，幾十年前香港野食就掂，而家狗也不吃<br />\n<br />\n用料又差，煮得又差，肉類更加唔洗講，霉到食落去唔似食緊肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7802f696b421e211e2f153065e23cccca1393766","tid":278680,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"有機會去日本既話去下人地中華料理店<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/095817_055ed8243727decea47ee9157cbb1052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F095817_055ed8243727decea47ee9157cbb1052.jpg&h=8010fdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人地舊牛肉炒出黎都高質過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7399ed17dbf7d76b712ead378d6ace1829b7b8c","tid":278680,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"雞蛋仔好撚好食喎"},{"pid":"28e09203411c2e9f0c467377446c1743f9d4b8ba","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一千個人代表所有日本人對全世界小食的喜好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁選舉委員會都可以代表全香港人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   統計學都唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7139d9962694121c5b20950f23c8408259c406bc","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心而論，幾十年前香港野食就掂，而家狗也不吃<br />\n<br />\n用料又差，煮得又差，肉類更加唔洗講，霉到食落去唔似食緊肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n<br />\n租貴, 材料貴 就令到食物水準大幅下降 <br />\n地產霸權根本就係兇手"},{"pid":"f1958468f1501b8722e854c5254675d17a714b8f","tid":278680,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"台灣街邊嘢就好食<br />\n台灣菜就真心難食到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2097b99f3e9d286301a202a568f3f4629aab25cb","tid":278680,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平心而論，幾十年前香港野食就掂，而家狗也不吃<br />\n<br />\n用料又差，煮得又差，肉類更加唔洗講，霉到食落去唔似食緊肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n<br />\n租貴, 材料貴 就令到食物水準大幅下降 <br />\n地產霸權根本就係兇手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係嘅<br />\n同埋個個開鋪都想好快搵到一嚿錢<br />\n變想韓國嗰種快速同cross over扮上菜嘅文化愈嚟愈勁<br />\n但都要香港人受先得嘅<br />\n個個都為咗打卡爭住去幫襯<br />\n但打咗一次就唔會翻兜<br />\n成個文化都唔健康<br />\n因為香港人本身就唔重視文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae2b902c299aa963bb9e96e3b2a9d709963e5bb","tid":278680,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平心而論，幾十年前香港野食就掂，而家狗也不吃<br />\n<br />\n用料又差，煮得又差，肉類更加唔洗講，霉到食落去唔似食緊肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n<br />\n租貴, 材料貴 就令到食物水準大幅下降 <br />\n地產霸權根本就係兇手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係嘅<br />\n同埋個個開鋪都想好快搵到一嚿錢<br />\n變相韓國嗰種快速同cross over扮上菜嘅文化愈嚟愈勁<br />\n但都要香港人受先得嘅<br />\n個個都為咗打卡爭住去幫襯<br />\n但打咗一次就唔會翻兜<br />\n成個文化都唔健康<br />\n因為香港人本身就唔重視文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0cbcb7425c2ef88cf5eb1c12465fc21b5dae2e4a","tid":278680,"uid":98551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"香港叫美食天堂好似唔係因為香港有好多好味既地道食物，而係好多有其他國家既餐廳仲要好食"},{"pid":"b219b25fc3f6450be6f697aa5578c06531d4a09f","tid":278680,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"香港其實係日本眼中只係拉圾第三世界地方"},{"pid":"91dbd93446695f6606d8d17f6a5517a22dd9afb2","tid":278680,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"日本街頭小食屌打晒乜春雞蛋仔缽仔糕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b640c82ebfa4755e1ada6ef7f1591c0cf3f9a2c","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港其實係日本眼中只係拉圾第三世界地方</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   CC 台:「唔好再講啦  唔想聽唔想聽」"},{"pid":"da3249032999a8f7fa812a60ab3448486e6f6024","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港叫美食天堂好似唔係因為香港有好多好味既地道食物，而係好多有其他國家既餐廳仲要好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁點解小籠包唔係台灣野 ,  但日本人又覺得台灣啲小籠包好味"},{"pid":"402c34373aee7bff24ef1002c27f420a4c1e1cc0","tid":278680,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cc 台 :「依 1155 日本人,  肯定無係被人收買架啦」  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美食天堂 都被評第 6 咋 ? 唔撚係呀 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩啫你"},{"pid":"713048c5cf70f951e76ee74a406257514344e2bb","tid":278680,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"CNN選出全球街頭美食城市 香港第七 坑渠油之都台灣未入列<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/212091/page/12?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/212091/page/12?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9183e6e383d792c9ce38b2c33b051e79287420ab","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港叫美食天堂好似唔係因為香港有好多好味既地道食物，而係好多有其他國家既餐廳仲要好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁點解小籠包唔係台灣野 ,  但日本人又覺得台灣啲小籠包好味</blockquote><br />\n小籠包上海江蘇先最正宗喎"},{"pid":"bd461fc40c709800248a38f651dd76c242e912f7","tid":278680,"uid":99175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"蛋撻見人見智  <br />\n<br />\n但雞蛋仔同砵仔糕真係好普通....無咩味"},{"pid":"0dbebaf2c489a3fb1c16db11038db3af76a99a07","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛋撻見人見智  <br />\n<br />\n但雞蛋仔同砵仔糕真係好普通....無咩味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我 3 樣都 ok 鍾意食 <br />\n<br />\n係雞蛋仔/格仔餅越嚟越畀班新移民搞到越嚟越 on 9 啫<br />\n又貴又多雜種味"},{"pid":"4c027a239dd9267503d0c9e69ef9c066fa017781","tid":278680,"uid":2801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"對於日本人 其實台灣都係等於中國<br />\n所以小籠包都當係台灣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有美食天堂係指有唔同國家種類嘅野食<br />\n利申: 3樣都中意食 不過而加質素係越來越差"},{"pid":"db79183471da24c1107d7fa3cf3cf98646b4bdd6","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於日本人 其實台灣都係等於中國<br />\n所以小籠包都當係台灣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有美食天堂係指有唔同國家種類嘅野食<br />\n利申: 3樣都中意食 不過而加質素係越來越差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本人先唔會當台灣係蝗國囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但可能會覺得佢地先係真正既「中國」   <br />\n<br />\n日本同台灣既關係係源自於當年佔領過一段時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c4b94238769777a163791f1128bc80a53b166e","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蛋撻見人見智  <br />\n<br />\n但雞蛋仔同砵仔糕真係好普通....無咩味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我 3 樣都 ok 鍾意食 <br />\n<br />\n係雞蛋仔/格仔餅越嚟越畀班新移民搞到越嚟越 on 9 啫<br />\n又貴又多雜種味</blockquote><br />\n大澳炭燒雞蛋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口感薄啲<br />\n北角雞蛋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似食緊蛋糕咁 半件就飽<br />\n仲有啲連登仔都推介 筲箕灣、媽咪雞蛋仔<br />\n全部都有蛋味 超好食 有啲軟啲 有啲硬啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不知幾正"},{"pid":"09e0ae333a46b52c1fbd7cf1119c930b9af703c3","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對於日本人 其實台灣都係等於中國<br />\n所以小籠包都當係台灣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有美食天堂係指有唔同國家種類嘅野食<br />\n利申: 3樣都中意食 不過而加質素係越來越差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本人先唔會當台灣係蝗國囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但可能會覺得佢地先係真正既「中國」   <br />\n<br />\n日本同台灣既關係係源自於當年佔領過一段時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本好似對台灣幾好 佢地兩個關係咁好<br />\n台灣小食好多都抄上海江蘇個啲地方 再加小小自己野之嘛<br />\n要正宗應該去返個邊食 去個一次蘇州 啲野又平又好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e89b1db9f21dc40ece5f1e8662fc050f887d75","tid":278680,"uid":26931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"雞蛋仔同蛋撻而家太多垃圾 好難搵到好食既<br />\n<br />\n砵仔糕係正 但太冷門 唔去街市都未必搵到 大部份外國人唔會食到"},{"pid":"b5f2ec9e8a8aeb90fe26dd63e1a80537acd2c276","tid":278680,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"其實雞蛋仔蛋撻真係麻麻地，格仔餅葡撻正好多，仲有碗仔翅呢啲又係超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b2de20e2563f4db5282ad441070ff487e359d6","tid":278680,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"踩港又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec4c98984c5d3fc4c2e90a63b38932b46faabc3","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞蛋仔同蛋撻而家太多垃圾 好難搵到好食既<br />\n<br />\n砵仔糕係正 但太冷門 唔去街市都未必搵到 大部份外國人唔會食到</blockquote><br />\n砵仔糕真係好難搵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇好介紹"},{"pid":"a482c812f1f78c50c78d6d8662d8832c699a1a17","tid":278680,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩港又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時真係唔得先踩,但班盲撐撚成日起哂鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日要等外國人踩下先知真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff79b85ab0fdc8cc0d2a7e377ef7e667b6783b6","tid":278680,"uid":101203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"其實香港憑咩話自己係美食天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254c3078712018bcae9adef3015b09bdf7490cb5","tid":278680,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港憑咩話自己係美食天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n97前旅遊局吹奏出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f118042f35ee76468f9bd3f336732243101680cd","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>踩港又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時真係唔得先踩,但班盲撐撚成日起哂鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日要等外國人踩下先知真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他地方好食 但我唔覺得香港地道美食差"},{"pid":"5970dc1d7606c2cb317c5a023b8ee3aac5bd2eef","tid":278680,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實香港憑咩話自己係美食天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n97前旅遊局吹奏出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兒家係咩美食都有 但愈做愈難食 愈做 份量愈少"},{"pid":"7ec6885b670bdc9f34dedbd467f4f09414e2b69c","tid":278680,"uid":4308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 論掃街香港好過台狗喇<br />\n唔明台狗夜市有咩特色"},{"pid":"82d35a5f1b80f5220648332860ce0b5543d23e2c","tid":278680,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"其實三樣都好普通 雲吞麵魚蛋粉仲好啦"},{"pid":"86f516266b5c5c69c619e6a24fb173ea46a33053","tid":278680,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"鬼咩,香港啲小食越來越垃圾,又了無新意...一係引進,一係抄襲,同香港啲電視劇一樣,仲要賣得貴,但質素參差,仔叫人地嚟旅遊食呢啲,玩咩!"},{"pid":"8447b9ed8157b656ac88497365ffbac09cc752f6","tid":278680,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣蚵仔煎,識嘅所有人去台灣食過,冇一個人係話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蚵仔煎煎難食嘅好難食 <br />\n好食嘅其實好好食 <br />\n<br />\n食過2次真係好食<br />\n一次係板橋，一次係零晨一點係逢甲佢即煎嘅<br />\n<br />\n煎到外皮小小脆 入面仲有蠔汁 正<br />\n<br />\n正如香港一樣 d 遊客如果係食龍x 果d 劣食 我諗佢一定覺得香港d 小食難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe4cc59549d7720ef0c96efd345221f783e7d23","tid":278680,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 論掃街香港好過台狗喇<br />\n唔明台狗夜市有咩特色</blockquote><br />\n乜香港個D真係叫掃街咩?<br />\n你搵到一條街係成條街都賣野食放街邊咩<br />\n老老實實 , 所謂既魚蛋燒賣雞蛋仔蛋撻.....我身為香港人都覺得難食"},{"pid":"d32e94f5cf6c19bc55a29596e34ca05143ed484c","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 論掃街香港好過台狗喇<br />\n唔明台狗夜市有咩特色</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   香港叫掃街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n台灣 夜市一份即炸地瓜球 , 同埋 d 玉子燒, 雞串,  都KO 左香港啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4a6425066928c0699cc4338370aae02a5816c3","tid":278680,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:13:46.000Z","msg":"香港輸其實係輸唔夠集中<br />\n<br />\n例如以前d 人就話去旺角掃街 <br />\n宜家你落轉旺角 得返菜街尾 兆萬中心果頭係多食店<br />\n其他變晒藥房 百老匯 金鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但問題係 果度間間都係劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又例如廟街 ， well 香港人都唔會去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n適客搵唔到好食嘅鋪 就覺得香港d 野唔好食<br />\n<br />\n台灣 日本d 食店就集中好多<br />\n有夜市 同小食街 等 <br />\n<br />\n香港政府真係檢討下啦，出埋d 垃圾小食車<br />\n又分散到全香港幾個景點，又成日轉位<br />\n完全唔遊客friendly"},{"pid":"d11992a02524dacbbeab7a768ffed4a21cae9753","tid":278680,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港憑咩話自己係美食天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最撚 on 9 係, 吹捧香港一個地方有各國既野食<br />\n<br />\n咪即係抄鳩人地啲菜式,  放喺自己啲地方 就當自己係美食天堂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食到香港既法國菜, 但都無法國既風味同特色啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}